  {
    "id": "f_csv_9b3648ffa2",
    "slug": "the-most-prevalent-form-of-slavery-is-being-a-slave-of-your-own-insecurities-or",
    "texto": "The most prevalent form of slavery is being a slave of your own insecurities Or exploiting another's vulnerabilities. Lust, greed and anger are the pitfalls of the short sighted. Long term business is not possible through lust, greed, anger or guile; it is done based on 'sustainable' relationships; And that is possible when happiness is your goal and each individual you transact with, is a 'strong adult Individual'. We need to invest in ourselves to make us one and in others to help them become the same. It IS in my Selfish interest to have strong, adult individuals around!",
